OpenAPI
Open standard for describing API.
Specification is described in YAML or JSON
It has a schema
OpenAPI tools: Converter,Validator,GUI Editor,Mock Services,SDK generators,Documentation.
OpenAPI CodeGen: Generate server code for 20+ language and client code for 40+ language


OpenAPI Spec becomes single source of truth for what API is suppose to do.
======================
